    Class and Description
    AbstractModule
    Abstract implementation of the Module interface.
    AptModule
    Annotation which marks modules This Annotation can only get used on non-generic non-abstract classes which implement the Module interface.
    Category
    Members of this enumeration represent a category used primarily in the module overview.
    Module
    A module.
    ModuleInput
    Storage of parameter values.
    ModuleInputSpec
    Specification of parametres of a module.
    ModuleOutput
    Storage of return values.
    ModuleOutputSpec
    Specification of return value of a module.
